# AI Portfolio Platform

Full stack portfolio — React · Python FastAPI · Spring Boot · Node.js

## Services

| Service      | Tech           | Port |
| ------------ | -------------- | ---- |
| Frontend     | React + Vite   | 3000 |
| AI / Contact | Python FastAPI | 8000 |
| Projects API | Spring Boot    | 8080 |
| Auth / RT    | Node.js        | 4000 |

## Quick start

docker-compose up --build
